node.text:
Loving a dog unconditionally is the bravest thing anyone can do. We recently lost a very special member of the Camping With Dogs community. @ambpitch's sweet dog, Ariel, passed away, but she stays in our hearts forever. Amber, thank you for sharing Ariel with the world so that we could all learn to be more like her everyday. She continues to inspire us to love fearlessly, keep going, and never stop searching for life's next adventure.
•
❤️ @ambpitch
Video by @leighccampbell 
Music by @sodvenmusic
